gentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"Run EvoMap status check. Execute: uv run python check_agents.py in C:\\\\\\\\Users\\\\\\\\16343\\\\\\\\.openclaw\\\\\\\\workspace. Report guan-guan status in Chinese: Reputation, Published, Promoted, Fetched.\",\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 60\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"announce\",\n        \"channel\": \"feishu\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1773885600000,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1773799200010,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"error\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"error\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 60012,\n        \"lastError\": \"cron: job execution timed out\",\n        \"lastErrorReason\": \"timeout\",\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"unknown\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 1\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"75761193-c4e9-4672-86b9-92f42f7c3fd0\",\n      \"agentId\": \"guan-guan\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:guan-guan:session-1773754048809\",\n      \"name\": \"每日进化日报\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1773756543606,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1773799442503,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"expr\": \"0 10 * * *\",\n        \"tz\": \"Asia/Shanghai\"\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"生成今日进化日报，发送到用户飞书。内容需包含：\\n1. 学习统计：今日阅读篇数、笔记产出数、知识库总条目\\n2. 人格增量：今日新增人格维度、累计人格维度\\n3. 能力进度：本周学习的新技能/工作流/思维模型\\n4. 效率指标：笔记/模板/案例完成率，与目标对比\\n5. 知识库更新：今日新增的笔记标题列表\\n6. 反思：今日学到最重要的3个点是什么？\\n\\n用简洁但丰富的方式呈现，数据驱动。\",\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 300\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"bestEffort\": true,\n        \"channel\": \"feishu\",\n        \"mode\": \"announce\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1773885600000,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1773799260024,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"error\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"error\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 182479,\n        \"lastError\":